## 7. SECURITY NOTES

- API keys are **never logged** or exposed
- All keys **encrypted with AES-256-CBC** before storage
- Passwords stored **in-memory only** during session
- Expires configurable (daily/weekly/monthly)
- CORS handled intelligently (Anthropic supports browser, OpenAI requires proxy)
- No central proxy (privacy-first architecture)

---

This architecture is well-designed for extensibility, security, and reliability. You can easily add new providers or use the router from any component!
